      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks for those. they're a good start but a bit generic for a high school level debate. can you go deeper into the \"rule of law\" argument? specifically, how a defender of strict enforcement would argue that failing to secure the border actually undermines the legal status of those who immigrated through the proper channels? i want my students to lead with a much more sophisticated philosophical point there.",
